It would be ugly.

27
00:01:19,786 --> 00:01:19,946
But.

28
00:01:21,004 --> 00:01:24,949
we would be able to wrangle it into something powerful and quite of a high quality.

29
00:01:25,109 --> 00:01:26,831
But I couldn't understand why.

30
00:01:27,893 --> 00:01:31,017
